						               													<description>Motim Pirata (Pirate Riot) is a fun dice game were the players are pirates in the same ship trying to take the ship from the captain.&amp;#10;In this dice game, every die represents a pirate that you need to turn on you side to make a riot and than take the ship. Rolling the dice you have, you choose one of them and use its spacial. There is three kinds of active pirates (dice): Thug (represented by the red dice; the one that can kill another pirate), Smart (represented by the blue dice; the one that can recruit one more pirate to you side) and Drunk (represented by the green dice; useless but you can use them insted of any other die when kill). There is the captain die (represented by a black die). When you have enough thugs, you can make the riot. You roll all the red dice and the sum must be equal or greater than the sum of the captain die plus his mates, you win. Otherwise you loose and your dice goes to the captain.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
